
Video via Philipp Schmidt, co-founder and executive director of Peer to Peer University


=Description=

'Meet Philipp Schmidt, co-founder and executive director of Peer to Peer University, an emerging, Web-based global learning community. At P2PU, study groups form and gather online to learn a particular topic. They do group work together and provide constructive feedback for one another. All courses are free and open. "Imagine a world where you could learn anything you're curious about," says Schmidt. "



